downloadTitle: Skype for Business – App SDK for iOS
downloadDescription: The Skype for Business App SDK enables apps to seamlessly integrate messaging, audio, and video experiences.  See http://aka.ms/skypeappsdk to learn more.
detailsSection:
This download was originally released on December 8th, 2016.
The Skype for Business App SDK enables apps to seamlessly integrate messaging, audio, and video experiences. The initial focus of the SDK is to enable consumer apps to embed communications from “guests” to Skype for Business users within an organization, via the "guest meeting join" capability. Over time, the SDK's capabilities will expand to cover other scenarios. See http://aka.ms/skypeappsdk for background information, tutorials and samples.
